Entry.JapaneseText: なあ、中身ちょこっと見るくらいいいだろ？
Entry.EnglishText: Hey, would it be okay for me to take a quick peek inside the treasure chest?

Entry.JapaneseText: ダメだ。マウロに会うまでガマンしろ。
Entry.EnglishText: No. You'll have to wait until we get back to Mauro.

Entry.JapaneseText: あぁ、気になるうぅぅぅぅッ！ 早く、マウロのところへ行こうぜ！
Entry.EnglishText: Oh come on, I wanna see what's inside! Let's hurry back to Mauro's place!
